<section class="card p-8">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 md:text-4xl">About Stockflow</h1>
  <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">
    Stockflow is built for supplier operations that need simple, reliable control of inventory and business cashflow.
  </p>

  <dl class="mt-6 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">What it covers</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Inventory ledger, deliveries, expenses, payables, receivables, and collections.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Who it is for</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Owners, operations staff, and system admins managing day-to-day workflows.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Delivery reporting</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Create PDF delivery reports and email them to recipients with history logs.</dd>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-4">
      <dt class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Access points</dt>
      <dd class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Separate login pages for ordinary users and admin users.</dd>
    </div>
  </dl>

  <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
    <%= link_to "Back to Home", root_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>
    <%= link_to "User login", login_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>
    <%= link_to "Admin login", admin_login_path, class: "btn btn-ghost" %>
  </div>
</section>
